        "product_description": {
            "value": "GEAR AID Tenacious Tape Flex Patches deliver fast, reliable repairs for vinyl and synthetic fabric gear. These ultra-strong, flexible patches are ideal for fixing tears in PVC inflatables, vinyl furniture seats, air mattresses, and other outdoor equipment. The peel-and-stick design makes nearly invisible, weatherproof repairs without sewing or iron-on application. Backed by a heavy-duty adhesive, each patch stretches and flexes along with the fabric and resists punctures for a permanent repair you can count on. Whether you're at home or on the trail, this compact repair kit is easy to pack and ready when you need it. Includes two pre-cut 3\" x 5\" clear patches. Packaging may vary.",
